== 背景与制作 ==
《破產姊妹花》曾与一部飞行员主题的电视剧竞标，并在2010年12月10日与CBS正式达成播出协议，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/12/cbs-nabs-michael-patrick-kingwhitney-cummings-multi-camera-comedy/ |title=CBS Nabs Michael Patrick King/Whitney Cummings Multi-Camera Comedy |website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2010-12-10 |accessdate=2011-11-03 |archive-date=2011-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026121719/http://www.deadline.com/2010/12/cbs-nabs-michael-patrick-kingwhitney-cummings-multi-camera-comedy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>预订剧集于2011年5月13日播出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/05/13/person-of-interest-two-broke-girls-first-to-series-at-cbs-sarah-michelle-gellar-led-ringer-shifts-to-the-cw-342011/9271/ |title="Person of Interest," "Two Broke Girls" First to Series at CBS; Sarah Michelle Gellar-Led "Ringer" Shifts to The CW |website=the Futon Critic |date=2011-05-13 |access-date=2011-11-03 |archive-date=2012-09-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AZunuWGT?url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/05/13/person-of-interest-two-broke-girls-first-to-series-at-cbs-sarah-michelle-gellar-led-ringer-shifts-to-the-cw-342011/9271/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这部电视剧是2-11年-2012年期间由[[惠特妮·卡明|惠特妮·卡明]]原创的两部电视剧之一，另一部为《[[三年之癢|三年之癢]]》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/11/nbc-picks-up-smash-prime-suspects-plus-two-more-sitcoms-to-series/92312 |title=Updated: NBC Picks Up "Smash", "Prime Suspects" and Two More Sitcoms to Series |website=TV By the Numbers |date=2011-05-11 |accessdate=2011-11-03 |archive-date=2011-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910164959/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/11/nbc-picks-up-smash-prime-suspects-plus-two-more-sitcoms-to-series/92312/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

丹寧絲于2011年2月18日被选为出演麥克斯一角。<ref>[http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/kat-dennings-to-star-in-cbs-whitney-cummingsmichael-patrick-king-comedy/ "Kat Dennings To Star In CBS' Whitney Cummings/Michael Patrick King Comedy"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/kat-dennings-to-star-in-cbs-whitney-cummingsmichael-patrick-king-comedy/ |date=20111127214216 }} from Deadline.com (February 18, 2011)</ref>2月25日，貝爾斯打败了许多资深演员，通过试镜获得了卡洛琳的扮演机会。<ref>[http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/nbcs-s-i-l-a-cbs-girls-find-leads/ "NBC's 'S.I.L.A.' & CBS' 'Girls' Find Leads"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/nbcs-s-i-l-a-cbs-girls-find-leads/ |date=20111024225014 }} from Deadline.com (February 25, 2011)</ref>

