==播出与取消==
电视剧第一季于2011年9月19日在《[[好汉两个半|好汉两个半]]》播毕后首播，并随着《[[老爸老妈的浪漫史|老爸老妈的浪漫史]]》将固定播出时间调整至了周一晚上8:30（东部时间）。<ref name="cbspremieres">{{cite web|last=Seidman|first=Robert|title=CBS Announces Fall 2011 Premiere Dates|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/06/29/cbs-announces-fall-2011-premiere-dates/96883/|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|date=2011-06-29|accessdate=2011-06-29|archive-date=2011-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110701095954/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/06/29/cbs-announces-fall-2011-premiere-dates/96883/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>第二季则因《好汉两个半》，播出时间调整至周四晚上9:00（东部时间）。2013年3月27日，CBS宣布续约《破产姐妹》第三季。<ref>{{cite web |last=Kondolojy |first=Amanda |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/03/27/the-good-wife-elementary-person-of-interest-2-broke-girls-ncis-la-the-mentalist-mike-molly-blue-bloods-renewed-by-cbs/175317/ |title='The Good Wife', 'Elementary', 'Person Of Interest', '2 Broke Girls', 'NCIS: LA', 'The Mentalist', 'Mike & Molly,' 'Hawaii Five-0' & 'Blue Bloods' Renewed by CBS |work=TV by the Numbers |date=2013-03-27 |accessdate=2013-03-27 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123030018/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/03/27/the-good-wife-elementary-person-of-interest-2-broke-girls-ncis-la-the-mentalist-mike-molly-blue-bloods-renewed-by-cbs/175317/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2014年3月13日，CBS续约电视剧第四季，并宣布于2014年10月27日首播。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbs.com/shows/cbs-fall-preview-2014/news/1002675|title=CBS Announces a Multi-Phase Rollout for Fall Premiere Dates: Preview the Schedule – 2014 Fall Premieres|website=CBS.com|date=2014-06-24|accessdate=2015-08-05|archive-date=2014-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729125027/http://www.cbs.com/shows/cbs-fall-preview-2014/news/1002675/|dead-url=no}}</ref>电视剧第五季于2015年3月12日首播，<ref>{{cite web|url= http://deadline.com/2016/02/angel-from-hell-canceled-replaced-2-broke-girls-1201698802/|title= ‘Angel From Hell’ Pulled From CBS’ Schedule, To Be Replaced By ‘2 Broke Girls’|accessdate= 2016-02-24|archive-date= 2016-02-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160224101159/http://deadline.com/2016/02/angel-from-hell-canceled-replaced-2-broke-girls-1201698802/|dead-url= no}}</ref>而第六季则于2016年10月10日首播。<ref name="CBS Fall Premiere Dates">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/cbs-fall-premiere-dates-2016-1201776569/|title=CBS Sets Fall 2016 Premiere Dates, Slates JonBenet Ramsey Limited Series|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-06-21|accessdate=2016-06-21|archive-date=2018-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180223214506/http://deadline.com/2016/06/cbs-fall-premiere-dates-2016-1201776569/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

